<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link606076" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=606076&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1108688-does-anyone-else-think-mr-simmons%2Fanswers%2F606076-no-his-vision-was">flag</a>
</div>
