<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1668400-my-edition-is-listed-as-having-311-pages">My edition is listed as having 311 pages, but only has 280 pages and ends with Chapter 16. There isn&#39;t any defaced pages but it feels like I am missing a chapter or two. Can anyone confirm that the Tor paperback is correct?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1668400'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F3979.Song_of_Kali">like</a></span>

