<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/33472881-andrew"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1406767012i/33472881._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
